            Advertising handle: 0x00
            Advertising random address: 3C:8E:56:9B:77:84 (OUI 3C-8E-56)
    > HCI Event: Command Complete (0x0e) plen 4
          LE Set Advertising Set Random Address (0x08|0x0035) ncmd 1
            Status: Success (0x00)
    
